{"tid":1395180,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［孔子啟超講香港］學如逆水行舟 不進則退！！！","createTime":"2019-08-01T16:16:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T16:22:46.000Z","uid":239530,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f86fba53fdd9ba4896010831d1c6f7c28dfbcde9","tid":1395180,"uid":239530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:16:09.000Z","msg":"社會就好似一間大型嘅個體 亦好似人一樣 需要進步 <span style=\"color: gold;\">若只求安穩不變</span> 則<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 一成不變固步自封 </span> 香港正面臨進步嘅一瞬間 但民主卻受到幕前幕後政權暴力手段政治手段 不斷壓迫剝削打壓 我們的自由一步一步由百米之外燃至眼眉被政權所消削 即將一絲不再<br />\n<br />\n啟超曰：「夫舊而能守，斯亦已矣！然鄙人以為人之處於世也，如逆水許舟，不進則退」<br />\n<br />\n不要再甘心被政權欺騙 為自己權益出發 只有香港政治環境變得更民主 不受政權打壓控制 我們所擁有的生活定必比現時優越<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山各自努力 光復香港時代革命<br />\n五大訴求缺一不可 逆水行舟以盡進為由"},{"pid":"bfaa04736650ce0af2ffc6fa8f521f4337d5ab9b","tid":1395180,"uid":239530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:16:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4bbb55f6a086c5f52f4010a5b8f518542a3ee0bd","tid":1395180,"uid":239530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:16:42.000Z","msg":"可能講得唔好"},{"pid":"ed5f9958ce9860e4d959857e88396acf76a77597","tid":1395180,"uid":239530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:17:08.000Z","msg":"不能安於現狀"},{"pid":"23d5a5cffdcc7e7b9ba73b9499910061bf8e7cad","tid":1395180,"uid":239530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:17:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb8dcb1df5b462423b6b9f3753b9abbea5592fad","tid":1395180,"uid":239530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:17:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8c922cbf3a903d92b4ae0bda2cd8316df63b53b","tid":1395180,"uid":239530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:19:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a193ea1f3af3110d0b4cb265c4f89f2ec5ef390","tid":1395180,"uid":239530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08